name: sorted(using:)
desc: Sorts a sequence of bytes from the digest using the comparator you specify.
declaration: func sorted<S, Comparator>(using comparators: S) -> [IndexingIterator<Array<UInt8>>.Element] where S : Sequence, Comparator : SortComparator, Comparator == S.Element, IndexingIterator<Array<UInt8>>.Element == Comparator.Compared
